  "name": "Hardware Services",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"hardware-services\">Hardware Services</h1>\n<p><em><strong>Settings </strong>&gt;<strong> POS Settings </strong>&gt;<strong> Hardware Services</strong></em></p>\n<p>The Hardware Service settings relate to the Retail Express hardware utility which you download onto your PC when setting up a new computer for POS, or going through the implementation phase. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000062015/blobid0.png\" width=\"742\" height=\"356\" alt=\"image\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 356px; width: 742px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000062015/blobid0.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000062015/blobid0.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000062015/blobid0.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000062015/blobid0.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000062015/blobid0.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000062015/blobid0.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000062015/blobid0.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p> </p>\n<div>\n<h3 data-id=\"installing-receipt-printers-and-integrated-eftpos\">Installing Receipt Printers and Integrated EFTPOS</h3>\n<p>For information on how to install a Receipt Printer or Integrated EFTPOS refer to the article <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Installing-Receipt-Printers-and-Integrated-EFTPOS\">Receipt Printer and Integrated EFTPOS - Hardware Utility Setup and FAQ</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<p> </p>\n<p>The <strong>Hardware Utility Configuration</strong> tab will show you all hardware downloads done on your registers or back office. These downloads will help you track IP addresses and which registers have installed hardware. <img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061975/blobid1.png\" width=\"715\" height=\"85\" alt=\"image\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 85px; width: 715px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061975/blobid1.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061975/blobid1.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061975/blobid1.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061975/blobid1.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061975/blobid1.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061975/blobid1.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061975/blobid1.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>When clicking the blue pencil icon for edit, you will have the option to select whichever registers are assigned to this hardware service. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061995/blobid2.png\" width=\"602\" height=\"351\" alt=\"image\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 351px; width: 602px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061995/blobid2.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061995/blobid2.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061995/blobid2.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061995/blobid2.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061995/blobid2.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061995/blobid2.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360000061995/blobid2.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>The <strong>Local Hardware Services tab </strong>will allow you to select/deselect the \"Forced Local\" check box. This is a technical setting used by us to force the computer to use the local hardware.</p>\n<p>Want more information? Find related articles here:</p>\n<ul><li><br/><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Installing-Receipt-Printers-and-Integrated-EFTPOS\">Receipt Printer and Integrated EFTPOS - Hardware Utility Setup and FAQ</a> </li></ul>",
